And this was the worst of all, which

41:47.320 --> 41:48.800
was learning about maintenance-related

41:48.800 --> 41:49.660
things on tanks.

41:49.660 --> 41:53.660
So I'm writing, I'm doodling, and so I

41:53.660 --> 41:55.740
decided to, oh, I'd come up with a name

41:55.740 --> 41:57.120
for myself as an author.

41:57.320 --> 41:58.460
I'll be Frederick Wolfe.

41:59.440 --> 42:00.640
