So we went golfing and you can look

45:24.120 --> 45:25.460
this up if you need to, because I

45:25.460 --> 45:27.780
couldn't for years had to actually look

45:27.780 --> 45:28.520
up on the internet.

45:28.520 --> 45:30.720
But what I experienced as we're, as

