46:02.580 --> 46:04.420
And I saw it sitting right centered on

46:04.420 --> 46:08.440
this very, very small gray oval grave

46:08.440 --> 46:10.800
in the ground, you know, and I walk up

46:10.800 --> 46:12.580
to the ball, it's right centered on the

46:12.580 --> 46:12.840
ball.

46:12.940 --> 46:14.440
I said, I wonder who's trapped my ball

46:14.440 --> 46:15.800
kind of, that literally was what I was

46:15.800 --> 46:16.040
thinking.

46:16.040 --> 46:19.300
Like, again, really tempting fate, you

46:19.300 --> 46:20.780
know, I was really tempting fate.

46:21.100 --> 46:25.200
And it says Frederick Wolf, German

46:25.200 --> 46:30.020
soldier died November 5, 1944.

46:32.180 --> 46:33.980
I had no idea who this guy was or

46:33.980 --> 46:35.380
