46:35.380 --> 46:36.780
November 5, 1954.

46:37.840 --> 46:37.960
Whoa.

46:39.440 --> 46:42.560
And I just dropped my club and

46:42.560 --> 46:46.380
completely, um, freaked out by the

46:46.380 --> 46:47.660
experience at the time.

46:47.920 --> 46:49.220
Cause I realized there's no way that

46:49.220 --> 46:50.480
could be, you know, coincidence.

46:50.480 --> 46:53.060
That's the night where I had the 747

46:53.060 --> 46:54.120
dreams.

46:54.340 --> 46:55.520
That's fascinating.

46:56.260 --> 46:58.160
Did you try to find anything out about

46:58.160 --> 46:59.140
the historical Frederick Wolf?

46:59.140 --> 47:00.040
Yes, and I did.

47:00.200 --> 47:02.900
And it was, he was a German soldier who

47:02.900 --> 47:05.940
after World War II was sent to Fort

47:05.940 --> 47:07.280
Knox as a prisoner of war.

47:07.860 --> 47:09.620
And he was involved in like a little

47:09.620 --> 47:11.660
