47:11.660 --> 47:12.000
there.

47:12.080 --> 47:14.720
And he was shot by the guards, you know,

47:14.760 --> 47:15.540
and killed.

47:16.180 --> 47:18.060
And, uh, then he was of course buried

47:18.060 --> 47:18.400
there.

47:18.400 --> 47:20.020
I don't know why he wasn't, his body

47:20.020 --> 47:21.240
wasn't sent back to Germany.

47:21.360 --> 47:23.380
I never found that level of detail, but

47:23.380 --> 47:25.420
it became also kind of this like very

47:25.420 --> 47:27.480
interesting connectivity because I was

47:27.480 --> 47:28.320
going to Germany.

47:29.040 --> 47:30.300
Well, I mean, what do you, do you think

47:30.300 --> 47:32.960
there's something apocalyptic going on?

47:33.240 --> 47:35.400
Because you, yeah, you, this guy goes

