47:38.180 --> 47:38.680
Revelations.

47:38.820 --> 47:40.680
All of those books are kind of notably

47:40.680 --> 47:41.600
apocalyptic.

47:42.020 --> 47:42.240
Right.

47:42.240 --> 47:44.100
You're dreaming of this sort of Armageddon

47:44.100 --> 47:45.840
like thing happening.

47:46.460 --> 47:47.480
Well, yes.

47:47.880 --> 47:49.940
And, and, and, and the ways I would tie

47:49.940 --> 47:53.840
that together would be, so the first

47:53.840 --> 47:56.940
apocalyptic, well, future dream.

47:57.020 --> 47:58.380
Now we're talking Ezekiel, Daniel,

47:58.440 --> 47:58.840
Revelations.

47:58.960 --> 48:00.580
I mentioned the person who walked up to

48:00.580 --> 48:01.540
me at that time.

48:01.560 --> 48:02.540
I, that's another thing I did.

48:02.600 --> 48:03.720
I filed that away and I didn't think

48:03.720 --> 48:05.480
about it much more, but it was always

48:05.480 --> 48:07.580
there, you know, I kept it there.

48:07.600 --> 48:08.820
It's going to serve a purpose later.

48:09.080 --> 48:10.360
I didn't think that at the time

48:10.360 --> 48:11.920
actually, but it did.

48:12.020 --> 48:13.860
And one of the purposes was after 9-11,

48:14.160 --> 48:17.100
I realized, oh, I get it.

48:18.040 --> 48:19.520
I'm Ezekiel's watchman.

48:20.180 --> 48:24.760
It's my duty to warn the people,

48:24.960 --> 48:27.360
which is really the quintessential CIA

48:27.360 --> 48:28.000
officer's role.

48:28.300 --> 48:29.780
I mean, it is in a very modest way.

48:29.820 --> 48:31.740
I don't want to make this sound too

48:31.740 --> 48:32.720
huge, humongous.

48:32.800 --> 48:34.660
It's just, that's what we should do.

48:34.760 --> 48:36.220
If we don't do that, there's not much

48:36.220 --> 48:37.660
purpose for what we do.

48:37.660 --> 48:39.620
And I realized it was much more specific

48:39.620 --> 48:41.700
in my case because my first dream,

48:41.860 --> 48:45.120
which I chronicle in the book, was

48:45.120 --> 48:47.480
Sadat's assassination on September 6th,

48:47.480 --> 48:50.260
1981, where I was in, I was there.

48:50.380 --> 48:53.440
I was on the scene when he was gunned

48:53.440 --> 48:54.400
down in a parade field.

48:54.460 --> 48:55.620
The interesting thing about it, I

48:55.620 --> 48:56.940
wasn't thinking about Assad.

48:57.220 --> 48:58.880
I didn't even know the event was taking

48:58.880 --> 49:01.140
