49:01.860 --> 49:03.760
And of course, given the time change

49:03.760 --> 49:05.720
between where I was at Fort Bliss, Texas,

49:05.720 --> 49:07.400
at the time as an army officer, it was

49:07.400 --> 49:08.620
right before I joined the agency,

49:09.400 --> 49:13.140
and where he was killed in Cairo, it was

49:13.140 --> 49:13.940
the exact timing.

49:14.020 --> 49:15.020
I woke up in the middle of the night,

49:15.140 --> 49:16.680
having had the dream, and I remembered

49:16.680 --> 49:19.340
it in every detail, watching in slow

49:19.340 --> 49:21.680
