49:22.380 --> 49:25.260
guns out of their cloaks and, you know,

49:25.560 --> 49:27.840
shot him dead, and a number of others.

49:27.940 --> 49:28.740
And I pictured this thing.

49:28.920 --> 49:31.600
So I couldn't verify any of that until

49:31.600 --> 49:32.280
the next day.

49:32.360 --> 49:33.500
Again, no internet, no.

49:33.500 --> 49:35.840
And it was reading it in the papers.

49:36.360 --> 49:38.140
Did all the details line up of what

49:38.140 --> 49:38.340
happened?

49:38.440 --> 49:39.720
Every detail, including the timing.

49:39.840 --> 49:40.760
It was just impeccable.

49:41.000 --> 49:42.680
And I did do one additional thing.

49:42.820 --> 49:43.140
I woke up.

49:43.520 --> 49:44.920
Was there an example of like a small

49:44.920 --> 49:47.140
detail that you dreamt of that was

49:47.140 --> 49:49.040
corroborated the next day?

49:49.040 --> 49:51.220
I think, well, the main, the most

49:51.220 --> 49:53.140
important detail, which I was tying into

49:53.140 --> 49:57.380
9-11, was among the, it's never been

49:57.380 --> 49:59.540
entirely established, but it certainly was

49:59.540 --> 50:02.280
in my mind that Eamon Zawahiri, who

50:02.280 --> 50:05.420
was, of course, the deputy head of Al-Qaeda,

50:05.540 --> 50:07.500
later the chief of Al-Qaeda, was bin Laden's

50:07.500 --> 50:08.180
lieutenant, right?

50:08.500 --> 50:11.600
He was one of the conspirators that pulled

50:11.600 --> 50:12.000
it out.

50:12.460 --> 50:15.220
And I, I mean, weirdly remember him and

50:15.220 --> 50:17.900
another guy named Saif al-Adil, who was the

50:17.900 --> 50:19.140
number three guy in Al-Qaeda.

50:20.140 --> 50:21.520
Now, he's the head of Al-Qaeda.

50:21.520 --> 50:25.220
So two of the people I pictured in my dream

50:25.220 --> 50:28.420
became the heads of Al-Qaeda after bin Laden

50:28.420 --> 50:29.720
was killed.

50:29.920 --> 50:31.940
And you know they were implicated in Sadat's

50:31.940 --> 50:32.360
assassination.

50:32.400 --> 50:35.180
Well, it's not 100%, but I did in my dream.

50:36.100 --> 50:38.180
But you can, if you Google it, you'll see

50:38.180 --> 50:39.360
they probably were.

50:39.540 --> 50:41.680
So it's like you remote viewed the event or

50:41.680 --> 50:43.120
something, or time traveled.

50:43.580 --> 50:44.720
Well, it felt like that.

50:44.820 --> 50:46.780
And it felt like it because it happened at

50:46.780 --> 50:47.680
the same time.

50:48.100 --> 50:49.740
And the more important thing is...

50:49.740 --> 50:51.080
Or bi-located or something.

50:51.080 --> 50:51.480
Yeah.

50:51.720 --> 50:54.340
Well, I had no, I had no reason to be

50:54.340 --> 50:55.020
thinking of this.

50:55.140 --> 50:56.780
This is the other, I think, compelling

50:56.780 --> 50:57.460
thing.

50:58.280 --> 51:01.420
Many experiences, particularly as you get

51:01.420 --> 51:03.860
into the Virgin Mary and things that later

51:03.860 --> 51:07.500
happened to me later, there was no logical

51:07.500 --> 51:10.900
explanation why I went in that direction

51:10.900 --> 51:13.160
except for the warning theme.

51:13.460 --> 51:14.940
You know, the warning, the idea that was

51:14.940 --> 51:17.600
building up to a series of serve as a

51:17.600 --> 51:19.020
watchman, serve as a messenger.

51:19.620 --> 51:20.900
Let's try, I want to go through the

51:20.900 --> 51:22.540
numbers themselves because I think they're

51:22.540 --> 51:23.120
fascinating.

51:24.160 --> 51:28.260
And, you know, I think of 747, you know, we

51:28.260 --> 51:29.780
were talking earlier, actually, before we

51:29.780 --> 51:32.660
started rolling, you have the seven-story

51:32.660 --> 51:33.860
mountain is by Thomas Burton.

51:34.240 --> 51:34.360
Right.

51:34.360 --> 51:37.300
And he is one of many mystics where the number

